587
01:15:26,253 --> 01:15:29,004
Alice, please don't do this!
Alice!

588
01:15:33,036 --> 01:15:34,728
Please.

589
01:15:35,660 --> 01:15:36,774
Where are you going?

590
01:15:38,636 --> 01:15:41,484
Alice, please,
what are you doing?

591
