needs evidence.
I have to ask you what you have.

600
01:17:49,256 --> 01:17:51,046
Adele's letters?

601
01:17:52,010 --> 01:17:52,903
No.

602
01:17:52,969 --> 01:17:54,081
Warning notes?

603
01:17:54,984 --> 01:17:56,774
- No.
- You have...

604
01:17:58,729 --> 01:17:59,809
two photos.

605
