you have absolutely no evidence.

632
01:20:26,755 --> 01:20:28,446
Deborah?

633
01:20:31,395 --> 01:20:33,184
Alice, what's
happened to you?

634
01:20:34,274 --> 01:20:36,250
I'm sorry.
I'm not crazy. I just...

635
01:20:37,059 --> 01:20:38,946
I went to the police station but
they wouldn't believe me...

636
01:20:39,171 --> 01:20:42,019
Then he came in and he brought my
shoes and he thought was nuts.

637
01:20:42,819 --> 01:20:45,667
I know he's your brother but
you were her friend, too.

638
01:20:46,851 --> 01:20:49,698
You remember when you said that
you were either with him or not?

639
01:20:50,498 --> 01:20:52,538
Well, I'm not...
I'm trying to understand...

640
01:20:52,610 --> 01:20:54,498
I just...
wanna ask...

641
01:20:59,138 --> 01:21:01,113
Was Françoise with
someone else?

642
01:21:07,875 --> 01:21:08,801
Yes.

643
01:21:12,577 --> 01:21:14,651
It wasn't an accident.
She left him...

644
01:21:16,418 --> 01:21:17,530
