anchors for Françoise's group.

654
01:22:04,543 --> 01:22:06,332
He killed them.

655
01:22:42,942 --> 01:22:44,917
Leave him, Alice.
I know him.

656
01:22:45,822 --> 01:22:48,572
You have to leave him
for your own good.

657
01:22:49,758 --> 01:22:52,607
Deborah, it's not the only time.

658
01:22:53,503 --> 01:22:54,484
What?

659
01:22:54,559 --> 01:22:57,210
I think that he was with
a woman, Adele Blanchard.

660
01:22:57,343 --> 01:22:59,316
And think that she was gonna leave
him to go back to her husband.

661
01:23:00,126 --> 01:23:02,013
But
think that he killed her.

662
01:23:03,199 --> 01:23:05,086
Adele was never gonna
go back to Michael.

663
01:23:05,886 --> 01:23:06,998
Everyone knew
their marriage was over.

664
01:23:09,726 --> 01:23:10,838
I read her letters.

665
01:23:11,741 --> 01:23:13,717
