669
01:23:29,980 --> 01:23:32,828
I think he buried her here,
at St. Edmundís.

670
01:23:33,820 --> 01:23:35,709
I need you to help me find her.

671
01:23:37,564 --> 01:23:39,452
Do you wanna go with me?

672
01:23:52,061 --> 01:23:54,034
I have a confession to make.

673
01:23:56,763 --> 01:23:57,877
I sent you those notes.

674
01:23:59,643 --> 01:24:02,578
I know about my brother's violence.
I've seen it.

675
01:24:06,459 --> 01:24:08,435
I should've done more, but...
There's no excuse...

676
01:24:11,356 --> 01:24:13,144
But he scares me.

677
01:24:17,979 --> 01:24:19,768
I'm glad you got away
from him, Alice.

678
01:24:21,916 --> 01:24:23,803
You'll be okay now.

679
01:25:58,616 --> 01:25:59,730
- Can I take that?
- Yeah, sure.

680
01:26:03,417 --> 01:26:04,529
I think it's here.

681
01:26:05,528 --> 01:26:08,277
He took the pictures
