682
01:26:49,623 --> 01:26:51,411
Oh my God!

683
01:26:51,638 --> 01:26:52,565
Deborah.

684
01:27:24,245 --> 01:27:26,035
Deborah!

685
01:27:31,733 --> 01:27:33,621
