699
01:28:50,418 --> 01:28:51,530
Alice?

700
01:28:53,782 --> 01:28:54,830
Oh, my God.

701
01:29:07,957 --> 01:29:08,939
Adam.

702
01:29:52,276 --> 01:29:54,065
She and I...

703
01:29:58,132 --> 01:30:00,019
