706
01:30:57,393 --> 01:31:01,288
Yet, not a day goes by without at
least one thought about the passion.

707
01:31:02,386 --> 01:31:04,173
Maybe was so
blinded by it...

708
01:31:05,074 --> 01:31:07,921
that missed all the clues
to his past.

709
01:31:17,777 --> 01:31:19,534
